The '''Embassy of the State of Palestine''' in [[China]] ({{lang-ar|سفارة دولة فلسطين لدى الصين}}) is the [[diplomatic mission]] of the [[State of Palestine]] in China. It is located in [[Sanlitun]] in [[Beijing]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mofa.pna.ps/ar/archives/3256|title=Embassy of the State of Palestine in China|publisher=Ministry of foreign affairs of State of Palestine|accessdate=3 January 2017}}</ref>

